com.madisp.stupid.context

Class BaseContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.madisp.stupid.context.BaseContext
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ExecContext
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ReflectionContext, StackContext, VarContext

    public class BaseContext
extends java.lang.Object
implements ExecContext
    Base class for all of the ExecContext implementations in stupid. All of the methods that can throw NoSuch* exceptions will throw them. The dereference() method runs instanceof Value checks in a loop and evaluates the Value until it obtains a POJO instance or null. The getConverter() method returns a DefaultConverter but this may be overridden by calling setConverter().
